---
title: Almond-Crusted Chicken Thigh with Creamy Sweet Potato Mash
description: Making crispy, almond- and panko-coated chicken is surprisingly easy when you follow our simple steps. The end result? Crunchy, savoury chicken served with a creamy sweet potato mash and garlicky Brussels sprouts.
